title: Jon Moxley
summary: Jonathan David Good (born December 7, 1985), better known by the ring name Jon Moxley,[lower-alpha 1] is an American professional wrestler and actor. He is currently signed to All Elite Wrestling (AEW) and makes additional appearances for New Japan Pro-Wrestling (NJPW) and on the independent circuit, chiefly Game Changer Wrestling (GCW), where he is the current GCW World Champion in his first reign. He became widely known for his tenure with WWE, where he performed under the ring name Dean Ambrose from 2011 to 2019.
